  "notes": "Single annual snapshot file, not a recurring monthly/quarterly upload -- re-uploaded whenever DOH refreshes facility/staffing counts. 'BGY & BHS' (main sheet) and 'Health Workers' (extra sheet) are two unrelated indicator domains sharing only PSGC/location/population columns; DEMO_POP is read from both sheets under the same indicator code (harmless duplicate, matches the existing per-file population repetition pattern used elsewhere). All ratio indicators are population (or, for BHW, households) per resource -- no natural 100% ceiling, so no dqc_rules are defined here; the source file's own 'greater than 1' Excel highlight is not a meaningful threshold for these values (see memory-bank/template_analysis/demographics.md Flag D-7) and real DOH staffing/facility norms are not yet available to build a real one."
}
